    <title>Combined summary - I do not support the BIP 148 UASF</title>
    <updated>2025-11-12T13:18:54.034708+00:00</updated>
    <link href="https://gnusha.org/url/https://lists.linuxfoundation.org/pipermail/bitcoin-dev/2017-April/014152.html" rel="alternate"/>
